<div class="page">
  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>Heavy metal is one of the most passionate and dedicated music communities in the world, yet finding reliable news, discovering upcoming shows and staying connected with the global metal scene has always been scattered across dozens of different websites, social media feeds and ticketing platforms.</p>
  <p>OneHeavy was built to fix that. We pull live news from the world's leading metal publications every five minutes, aggregate concert listings from around the globe, and provide a single free destination for every metal fan â€” whether you're into old school thrash, modern deathcore, atmospheric black metal or anything in between.</p>
  <p>No paywalls. No subscriptions. No logins required. Just metal.</p>

