  <h2>Australian Metal Scene</h2>
  <p>OneHeavy has a strong focus on the Australian metal scene. We list all major Australian touring promoters and provide a dedicated platform for Australian bands, promoters and venues to submit shows for free listing. Australia has one of the most passionate metal communities in the world and we are proud to support it.</p>
  <p>Our Australian promoter directory includes Hardline Media, Destroy All Lines, Live Nation Australia, Frontier Touring, Handsome Tours, Metropolis Touring, Secret Sounds and Soundworks Touring â€” covering everything from intimate club shows to major arena events.</p>

  <h2>Submit Your Show</h2>
  <p>OneHeavy offers 100% free show listings for bands and promoters. Whether you are a local unsigned band playing your first headline show or a major promoter announcing a national tour, we will list your event for free and put it in front of thousands of dedicated metal fans.</p>
  <p>Show submissions are reviewed within 24 hours. To submit a show, use the Submit Your Show button on our homepage or email us directly at <a href="mailto:increasinglyinquisitive@gmail.com" style="color:var(--red)">increasinglyinquisitive@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>Weekly Digest</h2>
  <p>Every Friday night we send our Weekly Digest â€” a handpicked selection of the seven biggest metal stories of the week, plus concert announcements and tour news. Subscribe free from our homepage. We never spam and you can unsubscribe any time.</p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>OneHeavy is free for all users and is supported by advertising via Google AdSense. If you are interested in direct advertising partnerships or sponsorship opportunities, please contact us at <a href="mailto:increasinglyinquisitive@gmail.com" style="color:var(--red)">increasinglyinquisitive@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>We love hearing from the metal community. Whether you have a show to submit, a story tip, a partnership enquiry or just want to say g'day â€” reach out at <a href="mailto:increasinglyinquisitive@gmail.com" style="color:var(--red)">increasinglyinquisitive@gmail.com</a>.</p>

